39
00:02:20,227 --> 00:02:22,186
you can just tell us honestly.

40
00:02:22,186 --> 00:02:23,507
Why are you lying to us?

41
00:02:23,507 --> 00:02:24,827
He chopped firewood, and I did laundry.

42
00:02:24,827 --> 00:02:25,987
We were both exhausted.

43
00:02:25,987 --> 00:02:26,906
Right.

44
00:02:26,906 --> 00:02:28,746
We understand
the relationship between you two.

45
00:02:28,827 --> 00:02:30,987
If you guys want to go out,
we definitely won't disturb you.

46
00:02:31,146 --> 00:02:33,626
But instead, you tried to cheat us

47
00:02:33,626 --> 00:02:34,906
and did it sneakily.

48
00:02:35,552 --> 00:02:36,466
That was really not right.

49
