If you two weren't here,

52
00:02:42,466 --> 00:02:44,067
saying "eh" and "oh",

53
00:02:44,067 --> 00:02:45,347
would I be sneaky?

54
00:02:45,507 --> 00:02:47,667
If you had an issue,
why didn't you take it out on us?

55
00:02:47,667 --> 00:02:48,746
Why did you deceive us?

56
00:02:48,746 --> 00:02:49,664
Yes.

57
00:02:57,306 --> 00:02:59,306
Alright, I apologize.

58
00:02:59,507 --> 00:03:01,507
I-I will try not to lie to you guys
in the future.

59
00:03:01,507 --> 00:03:02,347
"Try not to"?

60
00:03:02,347 --> 00:03:03,827
I apologized.
What else do you want from me?

61
00:03:03,827 --> 00:03:05,706
Then tell us.

62
00:03:06,746 --> 00:03:09,146
How are things between you and A-Si?

63
00:03:10,667 --> 00:03:11,787
Don't lie.

64
00:03:14,016 --> 00:03:14,987
Just so-so.

65
00:03:14,987 --> 00:03:15,904
Did you hold hands?

66
00:03:17,026 --> 00:03:18,306
D-Did you kiss?

67
